No. —.

Charles Anderson, Petitioner, v. William H. Moyer, Warden of the United States Penitentiary at Atlanta, Ga. Submitted October 20, 1913. Decided October 27, 1913. Mr. Lamar Hill for the petitioner.

Motion for leave to file petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit and to proceed in forma pauperis denied.
